channel.title: [562] Skill: Mining [562]
channel.description:
Well, pretty much i made mining for my 562 server.
I used AtomicScape[562] source and found the skills folder, all I did was pretty much get the woodcutting.java and change a couple of things around. like from trees, to rocks and from hatchets, to pickaxes, it only took an hour, but yeah just wasn't sure if someone thought of this :s
So yeah, thanks
Video if it's really needed, look at the bottom of my post.
